@apiUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

GET {{apiUrl}}

### List rooms
GET {{apiUrl}}/rooms

### Get one room
GET {{apiUrl}}/rooms/1

### List bookings (requires X-API-Key header)
GET {{apiUrl}}/bookings
X-API-Key: <paste-api-key-from-db>

### Create booking (requires X-API-Key header)
POST {{apiUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: <paste-api-key-from-db>

{
    "room_id": 1,
    "datefrom": "2026-05-01",
    "dateto": "2026-05-05",
    "info": "Test booking"
}

### Submit review for booking (requires X-API-Key header)
PUT {{apiUrl}}/bookings/10
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: a55fb52c3c91f1dacdcf07b1ad661dff

{
    "stars": 5
}
